# 721Land Concept 001

Believing in "Metaverse redefines the world", we built the 721Land Concept 001. 

721Land is all-inclusive and form-free. Come and explore the world that exclusively belongs to you!

######Designed by 721Land

An independent music label started in 2018, based in Shanghai, China. We do multi-style release, music event and communication & education project Eating Music Camp. We aim to discover fresh idea & passion on variety of music styles and build a good connection with music & life. Eating Music will always be open to the artists who is ready to define a new scene of Chinese independent music in future.

#About

At the beginning of 2022, QPassport, a new generation of decentralized identifier, and PlatON, a privacy-preserving AI network, are launching "MetaFireworks" NFT as a unique New Year gift for metaverse players.
                                                                     
                                                                           
 
#MetaFireworks NFT
As the epidemic outbreaks every now and then for the past few years, we have to reduce face-to-face gatherings and even give up reunion with our beloved ones.
Though we live in different places, the same fireworks make us one. Love has no boundaries.
It is our wish that the New Year fireworks in the metaverse could dispel the gloom of the epidemic and bring you joy, happiness and love.


#Rules

Available: 00:00, Jan. 27- 23:59, Feb. 2, 2022 UTC                            
Requirement: a QPassport account                                     
Limitation: only one NFT for each address per day                                          
Amount: 721 per day, total 5047          
NFT Types: 7 kinds
Can you find the hidden door?
